The paper discusses the intersection of social sensing and edge computing, which involves networking, systems, and cybersecurity aspects. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses the challenges and opportunities in this emerging research direction, which could fall under the categories of cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.CY (Computers and Society), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
